text: update s FROM #StmtAlloc s join ( select s.Stmt1D, SEMEAUNOCAEIONELIGIBEANOURE - 15/1ULL(SUN(i. totalchgs), 0.00) + isnull(s.TotalBillingAcntCharges, 0) from #StmtAlloc s JOIN retail_billing.bil.tbl_invoice i ON i.StmtID = s.StmtID 0 i tetatches 5 0 AND i.Invoice_Type_id NOT IN (2, 3) LEFT JOIN retail_billing.bil.tbl_invoice i2 ON i.invoiceid = i2.refinvoiceid AND i2.Invoice_Status_id = 5 where i2.invoiceid IS NULL group by s.StmtID, s.TotalBillingAcntCharges ) x on 5.5tmtID - x.StmtT0|
